description: Condor Ferries says high-speed sailings will not return between January and April next year.
title: Condor Ferries sailings to UK and France cancelled
title_page: Condor Ferries sailings to UK and France cancelled - BBC News
maintext: A spokesman said: "Condor remains absolutely committed to a fuller schedule resumption as soon as restrictions lift and travel normalcy returns; currently there is no certainty when any easing of controls will be possible."
